tory  With warm regards  Floyd H  Duncan  Col  Department Chairman  The Major Field Test in Business Though not up to our usual standards  the Class of 2012 performed well on the Educational Testing Service s Major Field Test Business  MFTB  Faculty Research Our faculty have been hard at work publishing research in academic journals as well as presenting their research at various conferences around the country and the world  New Faculty We are very fortunate to have one new faculty members joining our department  The Cadet Investment Group The Cadet Investment Group  CIG  was founded in 1986 by the VMI Foundation  The group s mission is to learn about investing  To do this  members serve as investment analysts and portfolio managers  Cadet Internships In the summer of 2012  ten cadets will be participating in internships at various businesses across the country  Some of these cadets are also doing the associated academic work required to earn business or economic elective credits for their internships  BGS Activity The Sigma Beta Delta  the Honor Society for Business and Omicron Delta Economics Honor Society were quite active this past year thanks to cadet leadership  Fed Challenge Four cadets participated in the Fed College Challenge in Richmond  Cadet Awards The Annual ODE Banquet to honor our top cadets was held on 26 March  Col  Bush   2105 Class Advisor Col  H  Francis Bush is serving as the advisor for the Class of 2015  Memorandum of Understanding VMI has established memorandum of understanding  MOU  agreements with five graduate schools in business  Alumni Survey Calling all members of the Classes of 1997 and 2007   Spring 2012 Newsletter  Field Test  Faculty Research  New Faculty  Cadet Investment Group  Cadet Internships  BGS Activity  Fed Challenge  Cadet Awards  Col  Bush   2015 Advisor  Memo of Understanding  Alumni Survey  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 